thread.title: Lindsay Li
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Lindsay Li

author: Lindsay Li
title: Lindsay Li
text: Every staff member I encountered was extremely friendly and helpful, and the pickup of cars was so easy! The rates were the best I could find in NZ and the cars were great quality and held up well during my road trips around both islands :). I highly recommend Omega Rentals.
